reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars First class part at a great price
reviews.reviewText: This filter is as good or better than the OEM alternative at a much better price. A careful visual inspection shows it is well made, with an excellent fit and finish. It installed exactly how it should in my truck and I expect it to do a good job. For the price, you can't do better than this filter. 5 Star!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It might look like a knockoff but it's a good filter.
reviews.reviewText: I bought one of these a while back to try it out and I have bought several cents. It was quality built and had a 5 Micron rating which is more than fine for me and they've lasted as long or longer than any other fuel filters and water separators I've ever run. The amazing part is if you want to research the numbers stamped on it the numbers printed on it and just dig around in the background to see where it actually came from you'll find it's a top quality brand name manufacturer. I'm not sure if it's okay to start name dropping here but if you're particular about your filters you'll know that the bright red ones with the black writing our top shelf and that's who makes these.
